  • Deprecated Classes 
    Class and Description
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.binding.BinderAwareRouterBeanPostProcessor
    as of 2.0, will be renamed/replaced as it is no longer a BPP and naming is a bit confusing
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.binder.kafka.BinderHeaderMapper
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.converter.JavaSerializationMessageConverter
    as of 2.0. Will be removed in 2.1
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.converter.JsonUnmarshallingConverter
    as of 2.0.
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.converter.KryoMessageConverter
    as of 2.0 all language specific type converters (kryo, java etc) are deprecated and won't be supported in the future.
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.aggregate.SharedChannelRegistry
    in favor of SharedBindingTargetRegistry. Will be removed in 3.0. Not currently used by the framework.
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.converter.TupleJsonMessageConverter
    as of 2.0. please use 'application/json' content type
  • Deprecated Annotation Types 
    Annotation Type and Description
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.annotation.Bindings
    As of 1.1 for being redundant (beans qualified by it are already uniquely identified by their type)
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.binding.BindableProxyFactory.bindInputs(BindingService)
    in favor of BindableProxyFactory.createAndBindInputs(BindingService)
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.binding.Bindable.bindInputs(BindingService)
    as of 2.0 in favor of Bindable.createAndBindInputs(BindingService)
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.binder.AbstractBinder.buildPartitionRoutingExpression(String)
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.binding.BindingService.getChannelBindingServiceProperties()
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.binder.ProducerProperties.getPartitionKeyExtractorClass()
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.binder.ProducerProperties.getPartitionSelectorClass()
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.binder.AbstractBinder.serializePayloadIfNecessary(Message<?>)
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.config.BinderProperties.setEnvironment(Properties)
    in 2.0.0 in preference to BinderProperties.setEnvironment(Map)
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.binder.ProducerProperties.setPartitionKeyExtractorClass(Class<?>)
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.binder.ProducerProperties.setPartitionSelectorClass(Class<?>)
  • Deprecated Constructors 
    Constructor and Description
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.binder.AbstractMessageChannelBinder(boolean, String[], PP)
    As of release 2.0. Please use other constructors.
  • Deprecated Enum Constants 
    Enum Constant and Description
    org.springframework.cloud.stream.binder.HeaderMode.raw
    - use HeaderMode.none.
